                            <comment id="14478518" author="paulk" created="Tue, 14 Apr 2009 04:11:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Doesn&apos;t seem to occur on Windows using Groovy 1.6.0, 1.6.1 or trunk. What version of Groovy (and Java) are you using?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
